{"tid":353313,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"毛記電視 100毛 Facebook開賭 莊家疑似被煲爆 08082017","createTime":"2017-08-09T13:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T12:37:20.000Z","uid":123228,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fafbb8af4a1de99657e88752ddaf6025f16961ab","tid":353313,"uid":123228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n昨日100毛個Facebook出咗個POST抽港鐵水，開咗個「港鐵壞車賭局」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇落無乜問題，睇睇下發現咗個<strong>破綻</strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>影片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzsCrZ08Ldo%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo%26index%3D17&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f5964b79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg&h=bf42827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每當社會上有啲多人關心嘅數學議題，我都會盡力拍啲片講吓，推動一下普及數學。<br />\n<br />\n之前新年我都計過吓魚蝦蟹嘅機會率（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyHocXb6q7U&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlyHocXb6q7U%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo%26index%3D10&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=80379f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyHocXb6q7U&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=10</a>）原來好多買法去到最後都係一樣結果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n普及數學唔係要個個人都係數學家，而係令大眾接納數學先，至少唔應該好似一般香港人咁，唔欣賞數學、憎數學，或者反數學，甚至反理性。最後好多嘢都討論唔到，淪為成情緒嘅渲洩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你支持普及數學嘅理念，我衷心希望你可以畀個讚，分享畀其他人，多謝你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb0ad3025dc8f9fcf48b84082e82a783f98d314","tid":353313,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"得喇知你叻喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c291d3329fb34d956564206b6c13914ec8791887","tid":353313,"uid":99941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:37:08.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打 有水準"},{"pid":"95e163cf7cd87a95c4d2c50964d71b503a54d585","tid":353313,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"好笑又唔係, 資訊豐富又唔係, 抽水又唔係<br />\n<br />\n都唔知你哂埋D時間做乜"},{"pid":"24f09909542121d4c0cfd7907bee7f2ef4675ce5","tid":353313,"uid":13165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"加油 諗多d生活既野拍 支持"},{"pid":"f7f858b8d8243e05b9718f61861a7c197f73bef9","tid":353313,"uid":123228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好笑又唔係, 資訊豐富又唔係, 抽水又唔係<br />\n<br />\n都唔知你哂埋D時間做乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n百貨應百客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講數學嚴肅嘅有人做, 但對數學無興趣嘅唔會睇,<br />\n好笑嘅又有人做, 但又好少講數學, <br />\n咁我咪溝埋做瀨尿牛丸, <br />\n其實都係機緣巧合開咗個頭, 手痕拍咗條片解答曾鈺成嘅數學題, 有人睇咪繼續拍, 我都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c862c73c038157342b541177e7885316de349aa9","tid":353313,"uid":113876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T21:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n昨日100毛個Facebook出咗個POST抽港鐵水，開咗個「港鐵壞車賭局」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇落無乜問題，睇睇下發現咗個<strong>破綻</strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>影片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzsCrZ08Ldo%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo%26index%3D17&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f5964b79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg&h=bf42827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每當社會上有啲多人關心嘅數學議題，我都會盡力拍啲片講吓，推動一下普及數學。<br />\n<br />\n之前新年我都計過吓魚蝦蟹嘅機會率（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyHocXb6q7U&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlyHocXb6q7U%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo%26index%3D10&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=80379f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyHocXb6q7U&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=10</a>）原來好多買法去到最後都係一樣結果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n普及數學唔係要個個人都係數學家，而係令大眾接納數學先，至少唔應該好似一般香港人咁，唔欣賞數學、憎數學，或者反數學，甚至反理性。最後好多嘢都討論唔到，淪為成情緒嘅渲洩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你支持普及數學嘅理念，我衷心希望你可以畀個讚，分享畀其他人，多謝你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持你<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"a86435b3765f320de571371b8d9ca5f1bf291ed4","tid":353313,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T21:30:43.000Z","msg":".."},{"pid":"b20405b8ecf674db717995ff2d5f72a9025cf56f","tid":353313,"uid":123228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n昨日100毛個Facebook出咗個POST抽港鐵水，開咗個「港鐵壞車賭局」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇落無乜問題，睇睇下發現咗個<strong>破綻</strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>影片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzsCrZ08Ldo%26list%3DPL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo%26index%3D17&d=C4m1Kk2qynx16K1dV7oruJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f5964b79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzsCrZ08Ldo&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=17</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F211427_d584b06595feae437c75cfac01d5cfa0.jpg&h=bf42827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每當社會上有啲多人關心嘅數學議題，我都會盡力拍啲片講吓，推動一下普及數學。<br />\n<br />\n之前新年我都計過吓魚蝦蟹嘅機會率（<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lyHocXb6q7U&amp;list=PL_CM4U5au2k1cfK2zSph8XOLqIjOPQmvo&amp;index=10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?